=== MOUNTAIN_HOLOGRAM ===
# id: 79
# title: The Mountain Shrine Hologram
# chinese_title: 山神庙
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

A holographic mountain rises from the floor, impossibly detailed — every tree, every stone, every waterfall rendered in light. At its peak, a shrine glows with golden characters. Climbing the holographic mountain proves surprisingly physical, as hard-light constructs form each step.

* [Climb to the summit shrine] {requires: hp >= 10}
  ~ gain_radical("山")
  "山" (shān) — mountain, peak
* [Study the mountain from below]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "望" (wàng) — to gaze, to look afar
* [Meditate at the mountain's base]
  ~ heal(10)
  "坐" (zuò) — to sit, to meditate
* [Scan the hologram's data source]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "数" (shù) — number, data
